Package: ggsegverse
Title: Easily Install and Load the 'ggseg' Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel",
            email = "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no",
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223"))
    )
Description: The 'ggseg' ecosystem is a set of packages for brain region
    visualization using 'ggplot2'. This package makes it easy to install
    and load all core packages in a single call. Learn more about the
    'ggseg' ecosystem at <https://ggseg.github.io/ggseg/>.
